OL,3,CMark Drakeford tells Covid Inquiry
OL,4,CBoris Johnson was like 'absent'
OL,5,Cfootball boss
OL,7,Fhas acknowledged that Wales could have
OL,8,Fbeen better prepared for the Covid
OL,9,Fpandemic, but said that "the enemy we
OL,10,Ffaced was not the enemy we were
OL,11,Fexpecting".
OL,13,FIn his evidence to the UK Covid-19
OL,14,FInquiry, Mr Drakeford also accused
OL,15,Fformer prime minister Boris Johnson of
OL,16,Fbeing like an "absent" football
OL,17,Fmanager during the Covid pandemic.
