OL,3,CMark Drakeford tells Covid Inquiry
OL,4,CBoris Johnson was like 'absent'
OL,5,Cfootball boss
OL,7,FBut he in turn has been accused by the
OL,8,FWelsh Conservatives of using his
OL,9,FInquiry appearance to attack political
OL,10,Fopponents.
OL,12,FThe inquiry has been held in for three
OL,13,Fweeks, focusing on the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment's decision-making and
OL,15,Fhandling of the crisis.
OL,17,FThe inquiry's counsel, Tom Poole, put
OL,18,Fit to Mr Drakeford that "isn't it the
OL,19,Freality that Wales was not at all well
OL,20,Fprepared?"
