OL,7,FIn response, Mr Drakeford said the ,
OL,8,Falong with other governments in the
OL,9,FUK, had prepared for an influenza
OL,10,Fpandemic.
OL,12,FHe said: "For what we actually faced
OL,13,Fwe were not as well prepared as we
OL,14,Fneeded to be. For what we thought we
OL,15,Fwould face, we had planned, our
OL,16,Fplanned response... did have a lot of
OL,17,Frobust elements in it.
