OL,3,CMark Drakeford tells Covid Inquiry
OL,4,CBoris Johnson was like 'absent'
OL,5,Cfootball boss
OL,7,F"It is simply that when we came to
OL,8,Fimplement the plan... the enemy we
OL,9,Ffaced was not the enemy we were
OL,10,Fexpecting."
OL,12,FMr Drakeford also told the inquiry
OL,13,Fthat, while he found Michael Gove a
OL,14,Fhelpful UK Government minister to deal
OL,15,Fwith, the "absent manager was the
OL,16,Fprime minister because he was never in
OL,17,Fthese meetings or at the table, and
OL,18,Fwhile Mr Gove was a senior minister...
OL,19,Fhe has influence rather than the
OL,20,Fdeterminative impact which a message
OL,21,Ffrom the prime minister would have."
