OL,5,Cfootball boss
OL,7,FMr Drakeford also said it was
OL,8,F"extraordinary" to learn that Boris
OL,9,FJohnson had deliberately refused to
OL,10,Fhold regular talks with devolved
OL,11,Fleaders during the pandemic.
OL,13,FThe inquiry had previously heard from
OL,14,Fthe former prime minister, who said he
OL,15,Fdid not want to meet with the first
OL,16,Fministers of Wales and Scotland to
OL,17,Fmake pandemic decisions because it
OL,18,Fcould give "the false impression that
OL,19,Fthe UK was a federal state".
