OL,8,Finquiry's Counsel what he made of
OL,9,Fthose comments.
OL,11,FHe said: "As you know I wrote very
OL,12,Fregularly to the prime minister asking
OL,13,Ffor a predictable series of meetings
OL,14,Fbetween the heads of the four nations.
