OL,3,CMark Drakeford tells Covid Inquiry
OL,4,CBoris Johnson was like 'absent'
OL,5,Cfootball boss
OL,7,F"It had never occurred to me until I
OL,8,Fread that that the prime minister had
OL,9,Fturned those requests down not on
OL,10,Fpractical grounds, which I could
OL,11,Funderstand, you know and these are
OL,12,Fvery busy times and he's a very busy
OL,13,Fman, but as a matter of policy he had
OL,14,Fdecided not to meet did seem to me to
OL,15,Fbe an extraordinary decision."
